Text: Interview thanksDr Kaminski Thankyou once again for inviting me to interview for a position in your Corporate Research group I very much enjoyed meeting you and your colleagues I was quite impressed by the excellent quality of the people and the entrepreneurial spirit at Enron The ongoing projects in support of energy and broadband marketing as well as insurance are very interesting to me I definitely would like to be a part of these efforts Thankyou again for the opportunity to interview with your group Sincerely Rodney Greene
